subtest read_only

statement ok
SET default_transaction_read_only = true

statement error cannot execute.*in a read-only transaction
DROP TENANT three

statement error cannot execute.*in a read-only transaction
ALTER TENANT three RENAME TO blah

statement error cannot execute.*in a read-only transaction
CREATE TENANT "read-only"

statement ok
SET default_transaction_read_only = false

